Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告，“路比根”作战失败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM依然在Side6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“塞库罗普斯”小队生死不明，完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，马上停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是中校的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐！这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得没有允许使用核子弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也记得，没得到允许啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙，要无视条约吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Side6并未参与南极条约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我的行动是将军管辖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的指挥权在我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业继续开始进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此刻格瑞那达由我指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你直接谈谈的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吉翁的MS旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何说要在哪里和你会面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么可爱的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是那个MS的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒这MS的也是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有残存的两名吉翁士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往市外逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么还记得的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，没有什么特别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的袭击据说有内部人的接应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于此事有什么想法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有想到是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白跑了一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人再行动的话又会有人死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是中立卫星殖民地的此处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会被吉翁的MS如此大胆的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道而不能回答，是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以联邦军驻留在此为名目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密在此开发MS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吉翁才来的，不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡人数246名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重轻伤者572名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨天的受害者的数目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不要再发生这种大惨事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不迎战，会死更多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没办法而不得不牺牲的人，应该一个也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是数目的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是惨，怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残存的吉翁士兵逃到市内了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好，被我看到一定打死他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在没必要在卫星殖民地内打嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦到底在干些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，那家伙，GUNDAM如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它，已被米舍破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也尽快逃脱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，慌话说得真差
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡提，西太卡死了阿！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米舍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那黑头发的年轻人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也战死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你就用那护照逃脱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想等警戒松了之后才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要马上逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想等一阵子比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听着！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圣诞夜之前不能消灭GUNDAM的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格瑞那达的舰队会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用核子武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同卫星殖民地一起轰掉的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那样，不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，快逃，逃走活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不逃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很老了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我很喜欢这个卫星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，是我啦，巴尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有注意你身后，走过来的时候没人跟踪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察有在找我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐嘛，吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人很容易就会死的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那些话，不要再去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的人就怪他们运气差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么是队长或什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有运气就会死！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在今天之内会逃离这个卫星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，那家伙，联邦的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放弃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时逃也是男人作为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这样下去，死去的人又算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过三天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不在圣诞夜前解决GUNDAM的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格瑞那达的舰队会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用核子武器连同这个卫星殖民地一起轰掉的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个卫星殖民地一定会被破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你母亲去旅游吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在圣诞夜前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙打倒不就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能办的到嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的，巴尼一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个怪物要如何才能打败？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是新型也不过只是快一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个渣古只要修理一下也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理之后又如何？你去操纵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连一架MS也没打下过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说再打下一架就能成为王牌的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一支菜鸟是大家的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被带来的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼一定是怕那家伙才说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！我很怕，不怕的话又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任你说我胆小，什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要烦，适可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，事实上是很强的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒它的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，这是窃听用的麦克风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防止你会把我们的事传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个在窃听的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么伙伴的标志，那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去就要逃阿，亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个卫星殖民地逃走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它人会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM，由我们来打倒它吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼是混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去警察局全抖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做会被判死刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，怎么不去学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同罪！死刑啊！死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？有什么担心的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好，可以谈谈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，巴尼怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都看不到他啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道，那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，如果，只是如果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙舰队攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个卫星殖民地要被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！我想我是不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是会怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怕能够忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独就无法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲，父亲，还有亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的朋友都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我一个人活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一个人逃了，我自己是无法一个人活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然逃跑是卑鄙的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗终究还是为自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怕自己成为孤独的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会去战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是我的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也属于那个人的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法决定谁对，谁错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为战争就会有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不战争也是一样会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的事在哪儿都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做自己能做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了些无关的事了，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到巴尼向他问好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷，亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！在这战时怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往法兰茄斯卡，一张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费用52O亥特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不可以进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！健呢？德尔可呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，回去！回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！喂！你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止些！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健，德尔可，喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是亚尔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天没来学校吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁的MS跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把学校破坏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？大家是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校的大家都没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是傻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS来得时候是晚上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说我昨天没去学校，我才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来了呦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在攻击完了之后马上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看看好玩的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是今天的收获
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道还留在上面阿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要闻闻看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那种脸嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会给你一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭嘛，振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对嘛，要笑嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，有齐穆中校通信进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击时刻决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月25日0时00分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞弹现在在装配中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐穆，真的要用那个嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反对司令部的决定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你很能干才派下的任务啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？这样装如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把过去到现在的事全说出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话会了解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么死刑嘛，为不让自己孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下不得了，马上逃跑才行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫你快跑呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在圣诞夜吉翁的舰队会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~！知道了，知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了，不得了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，你上次不是说什么肇事逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造麻烦的小孩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吧！可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你父母来噢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会死啊，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死的，我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰茄斯卡机MDW2O5班次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请指引乘客登机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登机手续于3O分钟后开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点什么饮料？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……给我威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍候！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也再来威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人，不要再喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的人可以，我不能喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威士忌是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双份！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3亥特5克鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费用我放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊！是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你所说，我正要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到乌鲁亚西的法兰茄斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想我这麻烦要走，放心了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那女孩幸福的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没病，只是稍微喝了点酒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没醉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能醉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要结婚的不是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛，说了一堆谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不想去那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰茄斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰茄斯卡不是最差劲的卫星殖民地吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MDW2O5班机登机手续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也是用马上会被揭穿的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那女的说了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我那时一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有把谎说下去的勇气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人，事实是很强的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，你赢得了那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢这个卫星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃之前告诉你有关爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离婚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样，爸爸要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要待到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈跟爸爸和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，不高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此以后一家三口一起生活哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连爸爸都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电话，叫巴尼的打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！是巴尼吗？巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，那个，刚才对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.28,0:24:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，救救我们好吗？巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩！我正打算这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.69,0:24:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！为打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.99,0:24:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备再做一次攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩！那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真谢谢，巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.50,0:24:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起做一定会很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.90,0:24:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩！会很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.10,0:24:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你，巴尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.71,0:24:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:07.14,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Can't you see that you are sweet？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:14.50,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh Let me love you so
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:30.60,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}见上げる空は远いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:37.09,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱えきれない梦がある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:38.42,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:45.19,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}创られた世界の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:52.34,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抜け出して　自由になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:58.67,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:06.27,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.68,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:16.58,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:23.05,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever

Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:26.07,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘をついた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.92,0:25:32.59,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに　怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.49,0:25:39.07,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧哗をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.80,0:25:46.76,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は　忘れていた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:53.67,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が　青いこと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.24,0:26:00.71,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが　嬉しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.74,0:26:07.15,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.25,0:26:13.95,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.71,0:26:20.44,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.25,0:26:25.84,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃

Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.30,0:26:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\pos(512,550)\1c&H00d9ebea}预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.91,0:26:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克其中尉，出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.01,0:26:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.21,0:26:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器不够
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.41,0:27:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.05,0:27:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林和它作战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.56,0:27:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
